node.text: Happy birthday to my bud @lamorne who off set shared a trailer with me for 8 years and on set improvised so many weird little short hand BFF moments like winne cece hand shakes/ babe babe/ and this strange ooooh I told you so back up now moment which encapsulates us perfectly. Love youuuuuu. Happy 50th! 💕

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Hannah Simone on August 13, 2021 tagging @toryburch, @howelltalentrelations, and @grandvelascabos. May be an image of one or more people, people standing, palm trees and sky.

node.text: Yahyahyah I’m an introvert who lives on my couch in my pajamas and binge watches tv for an unhealthy amount of consecutive hours with my cat inhaling chips and choccies BUT I’m also this palm tree beach fresh air living THAT life person and let’s be real both are equally as alluring/ desirable/ awooga awooga and whenever I’m deep inside one of those iterations of me I find a photo of the other and I’m like uh I wanna be HER so you know never content because I am jealous of myself.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Hannah Simone on August 11, 2021. May be an image of 1 person, dog and outdoors.

node.text: Being a strictly C loving human there are sometimes you can’t resist the D.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Hannah Simone on August 08, 2021 tagging @satyasees. May be an image of 2 people, people standing and indoor.

node.text: One of the weird gifts of my job is that sometimes they set you up with someone who your character falls in love with on screen and then you actually fall in love off screen. That was @satyasees (aka Shivrang to New Girl fam) and I. We were brother and sister in another life for realz. And we have maintained our off screen and on screen love affair… like in this amazing movie we did called Miss India America where he plays such a funny weird pageant MC. Spoiler alert: thankfully @taylorswift doesn’t scoop him up and run away with him half way through our scene. Love my brother from another mother. I also love wearing saris but that’s a whole other post. ❤️💙

node.text:
When someone tells me they want to celebrate my birthday in person* 🙅🏽‍♀️

*please make sure you tell me you want to throw me a party and send gifts and flowers and cards and make a big deal of it but don’t except my presence in any way aka a true introvert/hermit birthday 🥳

node.text: You know how some people put six sugars in their coffee and people tryin to be cute are like woah would you like some coffee with that cup of sugar I’m basically like that except my hair is the gratuitous sugar and my face is the teeny drop of coffee.. cuz I’m all hair with barely a face… is this making sense… forget it I need coffee please keep scrolling.

node.text:
I genuinely think if I took a 23 and Me Test it would come back 100% Cat. 
Breed: whichever type of housecat that is the most lazy who crawls into any scrap of sunlight on the floor and sleeps with the comforting feeling of being constantly mildly annoyed with all humans. ☀️ 🐈 💤
